{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": "",
        "content": [
            "要跳过此剧情吗？"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "新阿尔贝里亚王国领地·米罗平原——\\n位于与狄涅尔帝国交界处的据点之一。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120081_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "几天前，\\n帝国军向米罗平原发动侵略，\\n展开了压制王国军据点的作战。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120126_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "而前去迎击帝国军的，\\n是闻名大陆的白燕骑士团。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120107_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "为夹击帝国军大本营，\\n白燕骑士团副团长帕蒂亚\\n率领分队在干道上行进……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110335_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帕蒂亚",
            "context": "现在，主力军应该在米罗平原布阵吧……\\n从我们后方来的民兵队状况如何？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120126_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帕蒂亚小队副官",
            "context": "没有特别的消息。\\n似乎正顺利地在这条干道上行进。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110335_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帕蒂亚",
            "context": "知道了。不能大意。\\n目标是率先冲入敌方大本营！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120126_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "传令兵",
            "context": "传令！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120126_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "传令兵",
            "context": "来自主力军的传令！\\n前方森林里有伏兵！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120126_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帕蒂亚小队副官",
            "context": "伏、伏兵！？\\n帝国军发现我们这个分队了吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120126_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "传令兵",
            "context": "是的。好像在戒备我们从干道进攻，\\n早就设下了埋伏。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110335_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帕蒂亚",
            "context": "也就是说，我们想到的事\\n对方也想到了吗……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120126_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "传令兵",
            "context": "稍微兜回去一些，就有通向\\n北方干道的小道。虽然要花点时间，\\n但从那里迂回的话就能避开伏兵！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110335_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帕蒂亚",
            "context": "嗯，我知道了。那么全军……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110335_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帕蒂亚",
            "context": "继续前进！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120126_01",
                "120126_01b",
                "120126_01c"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "团员们",
            "context": "是！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120126_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "传令兵",
            "context": "继续前进……\\n继续前进！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120126_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "传令兵",
            "context": "诶诶诶诶诶！？\\n帕蒂亚副团长！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120081_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国军队长",
            "context": "来了……给我上！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120008_01",
                "120041_01",
                "120080_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国兵们",
            "context": "噢噢！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110335_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帕蒂亚",
            "context": "来了！\\n全军，听到命令前保持密集阵型！\\n守好彼此的后方！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120126_01",
                "120126_01b"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "团员们",
            "context": "是！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120081_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国军队长",
            "context": "哼……就这点人，没必要防守！\\n围剿突击！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110335_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帕蒂亚",
            "context": "那家伙就是队长吗……那么！\\n嘿呀啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120008_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国兵",
            "context": "呃！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120041_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国兵",
            "context": "呀啊！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120080_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国兵",
            "context": "敢小看我们！哈啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110335_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帕蒂亚",
            "context": "太慢了！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120080_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国兵",
            "context": "咕啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120008_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国兵",
            "context": "呃啊！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120008_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国兵",
            "context": "这家伙……太快了……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110335_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帕蒂亚",
            "context": "这样就能直取敌方队长首级了！\\n哈啊啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120081_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国军队长",
            "context": "什、什么！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120081_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国军队长",
            "context": "呜……呃……\\n我连剑，都还没拔出来……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120080_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国兵",
            "context": "喂……队长他……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120041_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国兵",
            "context": "被干掉了？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120008_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国兵",
            "context": "骗……骗人的吧！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110335_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帕蒂亚",
            "context": "趁现在！\\n全军，立刻散开！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110335_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帕蒂亚",
            "context": "歼灭敌方伏兵队！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120126_01",
                "120126_01b",
                "120126_01c"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "团员们",
            "context": "噢噢噢噢噢！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120108_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "民兵",
            "context": "嗯？大家快看。\\n白燕骑士团在和帝国兵交战！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "民兵",
            "context": "那就是……战斗吗……\\n我、我说，我们真的能战斗吗？\\n我们几乎没有经验吧？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120108_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "民兵",
            "context": "是、是没错……但是，\\n我们是为了战斗才来这里的吧！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "民兵",
            "context": "啊……是、是啊……\\n那么大伙，我们也上吧！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120080_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国兵",
            "context": "呃……这样下去会全军覆没！\\n撤退，撤退！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120108_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "民兵",
            "context": "噢噢！帝国兵落荒而逃了！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "民兵",
            "context": "嘿嘿！没想到我们挺能干啊！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120126_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帕蒂亚小队副官",
            "context": "那个，帕蒂亚副团长……\\n就那么放他们跑没问题吗？\\n要是他们向大本营汇报，我们就暴露……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110335_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帕蒂亚",
            "context": "无所谓。设下伏兵就说明\\n对方已经料到我们的行动了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110335_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帕蒂亚",
            "context": "先不说这个……民兵队的各位！\\n你们战斗的英姿，非常勇猛。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "民兵",
            "context": "没、没有啦……\\n直到刚才，还有点害怕呢。\\n但是，鼓起勇气真是太好了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110335_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帕蒂亚",
            "context": "嗯。今后也不要忘记这种心情。\\n因为勇气才是战场上最强大的武器，\\n是保护同伴的盾。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110335_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帕蒂亚",
            "context": "好了……以后我们就是同伴。\\n一同行军吧！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120108_01",
                "120042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "民兵们",
            "context": "是！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120126_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "传令兵",
            "context": "报告！帕蒂亚小队并未迂回，\\n而是正面突破了伏兵的拦截。\\n与民兵队会合，继续行军……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120126_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "传令兵",
            "context": "刚才他们似乎对敌方大本营\\n发动了奇袭！敌方处于混乱状态！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100018_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "是吗。真厉害啊……\\n你也辛苦了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120126_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "传令兵",
            "context": "是。但是帕蒂亚副团长她……\\n听说有伏兵后还继续行军。\\n说实话，有点鲁莽……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100018_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "是啊，的确鲁莽。\\n但也有其合理之处。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120126_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "传令兵",
            "context": "合理？为什么？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100018_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "有几点理由……\\n首先，即使要冒些风险，\\n她也不想浪费时间迂回吧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100018_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "交战前小分队要是能奇袭成功，\\n就能造成敌军混乱，减少主力军伤亡。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100018_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "再加上，最大的一个理由……\\n那就是让民兵队“练兵”吧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120126_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "传令兵",
            "context": "练兵……意思是\\n让民兵队打倒伏兵，积累经验吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100018_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "简单来说就是这样。\\n很多时候，民兵真上了战场，\\n就会丧失战意。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100018_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "如果战斗途中丧失战意的民兵\\n一起落荒而逃……会怎样？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120126_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "传令兵",
            "context": "根、根据情况，可能会伤亡惨重。\\n不光是民兵，就连把身后\\n托付给他们的士兵们都会陷入危机……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100018_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "没错。帕蒂亚为了避免那种事态，\\n想把获胜的经验分享给民兵队吧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100018_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "在战场上，自信会化为勇气，\\n而勇气会成为最强大的武器……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100018_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "虽然有点鲁莽，\\n但帕蒂亚非常了解战场。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120126_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "传令兵",
            "context": "是吗……原来如此……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100018_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "你是新来的吧。\\n先给你一句忠告……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100018_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "要是每次都对她的行动感到惊讶，\\n有多少个心脏都不够用。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120126_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "传令兵",
            "context": "诶诶，心脏！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100018_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "哈哈……好。那我们也出发吧。\\n向全军传令，前进！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120126_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "传令兵",
            "context": "是、是！立刻传令！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}